cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Archives World Map"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-05-22
description: >-
  A collaborative geospatial platform for cataloging public archive institutions
  worldwide. The Archives World Map (AWM) enables archivists, researchers, and
  citizens to discover, locate, and contribute information about archival
  institutions on every continent. Features include interactive Leaflet.js mapping,
  community submissions with admin moderation, 6-language interface (English,
  Portuguese, Spanish, Chinese, Romanian, Polish), OpenStreetMap/Nominatim
  geocoding, report system for corrections, and Docker deployment.
